      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 240ºC/ 220ºC (fan)/ gas 9 and boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and dice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes </strong>in half</p>",
