      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and <strong>soft cheese</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[275ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>creamy stock</strong></p><p>Drain your <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the<strong> drained mozzarella</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p>",
