    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>Tenderstem broccoli </strong>to a large piece of <strong>tin foil</strong> (or two!) with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Scrunch the foil around the Tenderstem broccoli to form a tightly sealed parcel[s] and add to a baking tray, then set aside</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-copy-1688483336589-x200.jpg",
