    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Put the dish in the oven for 12-15 min or until golden and bubbling – this is your <strong>creamy tomato gnocchi bake</strong></p><p>Put the tray with the Tenderstem broccoli parcel[s] in the oven for 10-12 min or until it's tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once the Tenderstem broccoli is done, mix through your<strong> chilli flakes </strong>(can’t handle the heat? Go easy!) – this is your <strong>chilli Tenderstem</strong></p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Leave out the chilli!</span></strong></p>",
